        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 9. Morphological character measurements. Hemicrepidius bilobatus: a) Measurement of pronotal hind angle in dorsal view. H. tumescens: b) Measurement of pronotal hind angle in ventro-lateral view, d) Measurements of aedeagus. H. memnonius: c) Location of ventral setal patch (vsp) on paramere. L = length, w = width. Not to scale." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4906788/files/figure.png" .

